{"tid":2168881,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"羅致光：若增加保就業申請限制，會令僱主不想申請計劃","createTime":"2020-08-22T05:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T07:18:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"775e1e4cd7007777bb76865e4daa43ba0eed2434","tid":2168881,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/UnbgtS2A0CJTCxLjEwQEKg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/CR-ESS-200822-0915.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUnbgtS2A0CJTCxLjEwQEKg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MzU5O2g9MjAyO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FCR-ESS-200822-0915.jpg&h=e66d6424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】勞工及福利局局長羅致光指，保就業計劃的目的是保留市場職位，若提高計劃針對性或增加申請限制，會令僱主不想申請 。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光：「這樣做的話應該一半僱主都不會申請，原因很簡單，拿了錢將全部一分錢也不留，不論他支薪多少錢也好，就將錢全部給員工，之後就沒有錢交租就結業，這樣如何保就業？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/羅致光-若增加保就業申請限制-會令僱主不想申請計劃-020645734.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89-%E8%8B%A5%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0%E4%BF%9D%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6-%E6%9C%83%E4%BB%A4%E5%83%B1%E4%B8%BB%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%B3%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-020645734.html&d=4FeJsexKtrFIFozdf5QThoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=6fc1a3e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/羅致光-若增加保就業申請限制-會令僱主不想申請計劃-020645734.html</a>"},{"pid":"612461d344d901ba64bc76d543d0fec9a6b4df24","tid":2168881,"uid":91771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T05:44:56.000Z","msg":"咁就改名做保交租計劃囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4523e1323970c531339